{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 865614831, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 60, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 13:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我教过你们怎么看日内反抽减仓位 你们自己看一下 我目前60%仓位 收盘收破5日我就到50%  如果不跌破就还是60%<br/>早上银行下午电力 今天不会有人来救科技了", "lou": 2220, "content_length": 134, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776923769}, {"pid": 865615749, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 96, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865615207,45974302,4257]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39810331]a471428019[/uid] (2026-04-23 13:59):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大我昨天4100清仓今天开盘买回人没了[/quote]<br/>卖要有卖点  买也要有啊  <br/>早上白线在上 放量 这TM怎么买得下手<br/>我之前把这种都分享给你们了  就是不学<br/>我这个成功率不说100%  但是85.324%肯定有的  不信你问问他们。", "lou": 2221, "content_length": 146, "reply_to": 865615207, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776924205}, {"pid": 865617338, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:17", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202604/23/jmQd62o-95gbK4T8S2j-41.jpg[/img]<br/>怎么卖 怎么卖 什么卖都和你们说了。<br/>你们一点操作体系都没有啊 怎么活那么久的？", "lou": 2222, "content_length": 110, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202604/23/jmQd62o-95gbK4T8S2j-41.jpg", "size": 4, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202604/23", "name": "jmQd62o-95gbK4T8S2j-41.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "8"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776925028}, {"pid": 865617909, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 108, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "如果你们按我之前说的  首先 不要追高<br/>其次  卖了电池  稀土 这些我明牌时间位置说减的<br/>然后 持仓转为半导体材料 AI软 航天  而且航天和国算明确说了不新开仓，也就是 当天绝对不可能加大亏损。<br/>然后不要随意抄底。<br/>这些叠加就是  整套的操作体系。", "lou": 2223, "content_length": 210, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776925285}, {"pid": 865618136, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865617756,45974302,4260]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39235785]Doh丶[/uid] (2026-04-23 14:20):[/b]<br/><br/>竟然还有亏钱走的，什么股这么神奇[/quote]<br/>太盛风能 暴雷了  没办法 亏了十几个", "lou": 2224, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 865617756, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776925383}, {"pid": 865618407, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865618256,45974302,4261]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62771233]极地丶之光[/uid] (2026-04-23 14:23):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，我想问一下昨天指数突破那么强势，今天在没有大利空的情况下这些钱直接给埋了，为什么会出现这种情况？[/quote]<br/>因为涨多了", "lou": 2225, "content_length": 15, "reply_to": 865618256, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776925510}, {"pid": 865619083, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 41, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865618871,45974302,4261]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66986098]moyu-eating[/uid] (2026-04-23 14:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大这种在你的体系是不是才是明确的减仓点，昨天那种喊了清仓的其实是侥幸，早盘追回来的就不说了，盘中抄底的那些其实就是硬猜这里该到顶了，这里该反弹了。[/quote]<br/>我不管别人 我的体系给我的买卖点都是确定性高的<br/>以前我猜50%确定性50%  现在我猜20% 确定性80%<br/>我只是不想死  我不追求最大利润。", "lou": 2226, "content_length": 119, "reply_to": 865618871, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776925802}, {"pid": 865619540, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 20, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865619313,45974302,4262]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60410084]Natsutoneko[/uid] (2026-04-23 14:31):[/b]<br/><br/>还有半小时 快收盘想跑的只会更多 看来5日线是守不住了[/quote]<br/>现在在持续缩量  不好说  这里机构不敢卖那么多 不然大家都没得卖<br/>只有拉起来才能换给场外资金  昨天就是这样。", "lou": 2227, "content_length": 101, "reply_to": 865619313, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776926005}, {"pid": 865619602, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865619445,45974302,4262]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39235785]Doh丶[/uid] (2026-04-23 14:32):[/b]<br/><br/>那没办法，最近鬼故事太多[/quote]<br/>我还确认了年报没问题  结果没躲过一季报", "lou": 2228, "content_length": 41, "reply_to": 865619445, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776926035}, {"pid": 865621110, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 68, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "长川1000E以上就不是我的理解范围了  我会把所有利润都出  留本金在里面<br/>这个东西我说了算<br/><br/>这段时间难做 个股进场出场的点位和时间我基本都这里说了  之后我尽量不说我没做好成本的个股了 容易搞坏我的图形。", "lou": 2229, "content_length": 183, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776926714}, {"pid": 865621979, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 14:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865621780,45974302,4265]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=331181]xhox[/uid] (2026-04-23 14:50):[/b]<br/><br/>那就剩下 材料和ai软，我刚才把ai软卖了，结果尾盘又砸了[/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202604/23/jmQd62o-4h1zK7T1kScm-1e.jpg[/img]<br/>不要怕  等下来还能做", "lou": 2230, "content_length": 62, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202604/23/jmQd62o-4h1zK7T1kScm-1e.jpg", "size": 8, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202604/23", "name": "jmQd62o-4h1zK7T1kScm-1e.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 865621780, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776927089}, {"pid": 865645895, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 62, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 17:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "对了 这波双跌停2个票都是挣钱的吧  这个方法成功率如何。", "lou": 2231, "content_length": 51, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776937501}, {"pid": 865646686, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 17:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865646568,45974302,4280]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989744]两极反转我要成功[/uid] (2026-04-23 17:50):[/b]<br/><br/>牛 昨天翘板跟着地板打入英子，早上开盘就跑了，认知和心态还是不够清晰，昨晚复盘知道开盘可能是最低点，主力还会向上拉升震荡，开盘还是卖在了最低点，不然可以赚5个多点的[s:ac:喘][/quote]<br/>怎么卖  多少卖 我之前都详细讲过", "lou": 2232, "content_length": 33, "reply_to": 865646568, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776937865}, {"pid": 865647465, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 17:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865646714,45974302,4280]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67141495]嘉然今天亏好多[/uid] (2026-04-23 17:51):[/b]<br/><br/>圣阳亏了，昨天-6买的，今天早上十分钟没起色，电池也半死不活就跑了，总计-5[/quote]<br/>你知道你为什么拿不住么  因为你不是开板的时候买的 开盘你一旦继续大亏 你就拿不住了", "lou": 2233, "content_length": 81, "reply_to": 865646714, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776938238}, {"pid": 865650370, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 42, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-23 18:22", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865649930,45974302,4281]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66996623]海豹x[/uid] (2026-04-23 18:18):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大牛逼，据我观察的5次，胜率是100%<br/>只实操了这波，英维克吃了4个点跑路<br/>卖在最高点了<br/>[img]./mon_202604/23/jmQd62o-a21jKdT1kScw-bq.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>嗯 算不错了  正常收益就是3-5个点  <br/>所以为什么我的方法条件非常苛刻 只有这么苛刻还能达成的票才能有足够的成功率<br/>在这个市场成功率高不是一件容易的事情", "lou": 2234, "content_length": 142, "reply_to": 865649930, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776939730}, {"pid": 865713301, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 128, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-24 09:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "前天你们叼杠我  我不挑你们理 <br/>今天能不能给我道歉", "lou": 2235, "content_length": 44, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776995173}, {"pid": 865714391, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-24 09:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=865713900,45974302,4298]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64921013]天黑就回[/uid] (2026-04-24 09:49):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大帅啊，我现在半仓，但是还是痛，本来应该更痛[/quote]<br/>像我这种留材料的 今天甚至不会痛", "lou": 2236, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 865713900, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776995548}, {"pid": 865714905, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 